                        <title xml:lang="en">Grammatical notes on the Pentateuch, Joshua, and Judges (fragment)</title>
                        
                        
                        
                        <note>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>This fragment is probably Abu al-Faraj's work entitled <quote xml:lang="jrb"> תפסיר אלאלפאט’ אלעצבה</quote>.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>In the Pentateuch, the beginning of a weekly section is usually indicated in the margin by the word פרש enclosed within a pen and ink design.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
                     
                     
                     
