                        <locus from="22r" to="89v"/>
                        
                        
                        
                        <title xml:lang="en">Commentary on 1Samuel 9:25-27, 11:5-14:23, 31-33:9.</title>
                        
                        
                        
                        <note>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>The Hebrew text of 1Sam. 10:1-4, 11:7-14:28, 14:36-18:12 is embodied, each verse being followed by an Arabic translation.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Part of the verses is punctuated and accentuated.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Parts of the Arabic translation is written in red ink.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Some masoretic notes are marked in the margin.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Lacunae after folios 22 and46.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <author>
                           
                           
                           
